Python dependency prefix.

This prefix extends llvm_dependencies for building Python and Python-adjacent
tools.

Target triple: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Included additional dependency sources:
  curl @CURL_VERSION@
  util-linux/libuuid @UTIL_LINUX_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  expat @EXPAT_VERSION@
  sqlite @SQLITE_VERSION@
  gdbm @GDBM_VERSION@ (Linux only)
  libxslt @LIBXSLT_VERSION@
  icu4c @ICU_VERSION@
